description:
TermPointToGNBDU: This table tracks the association between terminal points and gNB-DUs, including their operational status, IP addresses, and identifiers.

- **dateTime:** Timestamp of the data record.
- **Area_Name:** Name of the geographical area.
- **CellId:** Unique identifier of the cell site.
- **Id2:** Redundant cell identifier (appears to duplicate CellId).
- **Id3:**  Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear from sample data).
- **vsDataType:** Data type identifier.
- **vsDataFormatVersion:** Version of the data format.
- **TermPointToGNBDU.usedIpAddress:** IP address used by the terminal point to communicate with the gNB-DU.
- **TermPointToGNBDU.gNBDUId:** Unique identifier of the gNB-DU.
- **TermPointToGNBDU.operationalState:** Operational state of the connection (e.g., ENABLED, DISABLED).
- **TermPointToGNBDU.availabilityStatus:** Availability status of the connection (appears sparsely populated).
- **TermPointToGNBDU.gNBDUName:** Name of the gNB-DU (appears sparsely populated).
- **TermPointToGNBDU.termPointToGNBDUId:** Unique identifier of the TermPointToGNBDU association.
